    "For each training, 20% of the portion from the training set is used for validation, and this part is not included in the training.",
    "In this paper, the model framework and parameters are set up mainly based on the literature [28] [29] [30] and adjusted through multiple experimental tests and personal experience.",
    "The TCN framework composed of 5 stacked TCN-ECA modules is used in this experiment.",
    "There are 32 filters in each module, and the dilation coefficient is 1, 2, 4, 8, 16.",
